# QA Practice Project Parabank

[https://parabank.parasoft.com/parabank/](https://parabank.parasoft.com/parabank/)

## Objective

Practice manual QA testing by writing structured test cases and identifying potential issues.

## Tested Features

* User Registration
* Login
* Transfer Funds
* Bill Pay

---

## Test Case User Registration

**Test Case ID:** TC_001
**Title:** Register

**Steps:**

1. Go to main home page
2. Navigate to Register link
3. Click "Register"
4. Register with valid data
5. Verify successful account creation

**Expected Result:**
User is successfully registered and account is created. Required fields validation should prevent submission when mandatory fields are empty.

**Actual Result:**
User is successfully registered when valid data is provided. Required field validation appears to work when fields are left blank.

**Status:**
PASS

---

## Test Case Login

**Test Case ID:** TC_002
**Title:** Login

**Steps:**

1. Go to main home page
2. Navigate to Login
3. Enter valid username/password
4. Click "Login"
5. Verify successful login

**Expected Result:**
User should be logged in successfully with valid credentials. Invalid credentials should show a validation error message.

**Actual Result:**
System displays error message: “An internal error has occurred and has been logged” when using both valid and invalid credentials. Login functionality is not accessible.

**Status:**
BLOCKED

**Notes:**
Login functionality is not working as expected, preventing further testing of dependent modules.

